OL,3,CSpeeding driver who caused fatal crash
OL,4,Con M27 in Hampshire jailed
OL,6,FA speeding driver who caused a fatal
OL,7,Fcrash on the M27 in Hampshire has been
OL,8,Fjailed.
OL,10,FRoss Neiland, 38, from Littlehampton,
OL,11,Fwas driving a black Volkswagen Polo at
OL,12,Fspeeds of 90mph in treacherous weather
OL,13,Fconditions on 21 February last year.
OL,15,FHe lost control along the westbound
OL,16,Fcarriageway of the motorway and
OL,17,Fcollided with a Nissan Juke and a
OL,18,Florry.
