OL,3,CSpeeding driver who caused fatal crash
OL,4,Con M27 in Hampshire jailed
OL,6,F36-year-old Michal Kaminski from
OL,7,FSalisbury, Wiltshire, was pronounced
OL,8,Fdead at the scene after his lorry was
OL,9,Fforced off the carriageway and into
OL,10,Fthe metal support of an overhead
OL,11,Fgantry.
OL,13,FNeiland attempted to flee the scene
OL,14,Fand had to be stopped by members of
OL,15,Fthe public on the grass verge at the
OL,16,Fside of the motorway.
