OL,4,Con M27 in Hampshire jailed
OL,6,FThe court heard Neiland was in
OL,7,Fpossession of stolen goods when he was
OL,8,Farrested, including meat, cheese and
OL,9,Flaundry detergent, which had been
OL,10,Fshoplifted earlier that day.
OL,12,FThe carriageway was closed for two
OL,13,Fdays as work was carried out to make
OL,14,Fsure the overhead gantry was safe
OL,15,Ffollowing the crash.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
