OL,4,Con M27 in Hampshire jailed
OL,6,FPhil Hanham QPM, lead investigating
OL,7,Fofficer for this case, said: "Michal
OL,8,Fwas innocently going about his daily
OL,9,Fwork when his life was cruelly cut
OL,10,Fshort that day by the selfish actions
OL,11,Fof another driver.
OL,13,F"The dash cam footage of Neiland
OL,14,Fspeeding, despite the heavy rain, is
OL,15,Fextremely shocking to view.
OL,17,F"He clearly had absolutely no regard
OL,18,Ffor the safety of himself, his
OL,19,Fpassengers and other road users.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
