OL,4,Con M27 in Hampshire jailed
OL,6,F"I would like to pay tribute to the
OL,7,Ffamily and friends of Michal who have
OL,8,Fremained so dignified throughout the
OL,9,Finvestigation and court proceedings.
OL,11,F"These scenes are incredibly difficult
OL,12,Fand upsetting for the members of the
OL,13,Femergency services that are called to
OL,14,Fthem while doing their jobs.
OL,16,F"The motorists who were nearby when
OL,17,Fthe collision happened were extremely
OL,18,Fpatient and understanding and I want
OL,19,Fto thank the public for their support
OL,20,Fduring the two days it took to get the
OL,21,Fcarriageway back open.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
