OL,3,CSpeeding driver who caused fatal crash
OL,4,Con M27 in Hampshire jailed
OL,6,F"I would also like to thank all the
OL,7,Fstaff from all the emergency services
OL,8,Fand partners who worked so closely to
OL,9,Fbring this complex investigation to a
OL,10,Fclose.
OL,12,F"In particular I must thank DC Ian
OL,13,FStevens and PC Rob Giles for their
OL,14,Fexcellent investigation and case
OL,15,Fpresentation, which left Neiland with
OL,16,Fno other option than to plead guilty
OL,17,Fto all offences.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
